      "content": "i get that, but doctors always make such a big deal out of everything. i've seen a lot of wellness influencers say that massive doses are the best way to \"load\" your system and that the body just processes the excess naturally. if i only do it for like 14 days, isn't the risk of toxicity pretty much zero? i just really want to feel better fast without the whole medical hassle.",
